WPOKE again."},{"version":"gold","text":"If the tail-biting SHELLDER is thrown off in a harsh battle, it reverts to being an ordi\u00ad nary SLOWPOKE."},{"version":"silver","text":"Naturally dull to begin with, it lost its ability to feel pain due to SHELLDER's seeping poison."},{"version":"crystal","text":"An attached SHELLDER won't let go because of the tasty flavor that oozes out of its tail."},{"version":"ruby","text":"SLOWBRO\u2019s tail has a SHELLDER firmly attached with a bite. As a result, the tail can\u2019t be used for fishing anymore. This causes SLOWBRO to grudgingly swim and catch prey instead."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"SLOWBRO\u2019s tail has a SHELLDER firmly attached with a bite. As a result, the tail can\u2019t be used for fishing anymore. This causes SLOWBRO to grudgingly swim and catch prey instead."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Its tail has a SHELLDER firmly attached with a bite. As a result, the tail can\u2019t be used for fishing anymore. This forces it to reluctantly swim and catch prey."},{"version":"firered","text":"When a SLOWPOKE went hunting in the sea, its tail was bitten by a SHELLDER. That made it evolve into SLOWBRO."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"The SHELLDER that latches onto SLOWPOKE\u2019s tail is said to feed on the host\u2019s leftover scraps."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Though usually dim witted, it seems to become inspired if the SHELLDER on its tail bites down."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Though usually dim witted, it seems to become inspired if the SHELLDER on its tail bites down."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Though usually dim witted, it seems to become inspired if the SHELLDER on its tail bites down."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"If the tail-biting SHELLDER is thrown off in a harsh battle, it reverts to being an ordinary SLOWPOKE."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Naturally dull to begin with, it lost its ability to feel pain due to SHELLDER\u2019s seeping poison."},{"version":"black","text":"Though usually dim witted, it seems to become inspired if the Shellder on its tail bites down."},{"version":"white","text":"Though usually dim witted, it seems to become inspired if the Shellder on its tail bites down."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Though usually dim witted, it seems to become inspired if the Shellder on its tail bites down."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Though usually dim witted, it seems to become inspired if the Shellder on its tail bites down."},{"version":"x","text":"An attached Shellder won\u2019t let go because of the tasty flavor that oozes out of its tail."},{"version":"y","text":"When a Slowpoke went hunting in the sea, its tail was bitten by a Shellder. That made it evolve into Slowbro."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Slowbro\u2019s tail has a Shellder firmly attached with a bite. As a result, the tail can\u2019t be used for fishing anymore. This causes Slowbro to grudgingly swim and catch prey instead."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Slowbro\u2019s tail has a Shellder firmly attached with a bite. As a result, the tail can\u2019t be used for fishing anymore. This causes Slowbro to grudgingly swim and catch prey instead."},{"version":"sun","text":"It spaces out while gazing at the sea. With Shellder\u2019s poison flowing through its body, it becomes even spacier."},{"version":"moon","text":"Whenever Shellder bites down hard on its tail, it gives Slowbro a flash of inspiration...which it forgets a moment later."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"Spacing out is basically all it does. It turns back into Slowpoke if its tail, along with Shellder, breaks off."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Shellder, in its greed to suck out more and more sweetness from Slowbro\u2019s tail, has metamorphosed into a spiral-shaped shell."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Lives lazily by the sea. If the Shellder on its tail comes off, it becomes a Slowpoke again."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Lives lazily by the sea. If the Shellder on its tail comes off, it becomes a Slowpoke again."},{"version":"sword","text":"Slowpoke became Slowbro when a Shellder bit on to its tail. Sweet flavors seeping from the tail make the Shellder feel as if its life is a dream."},{"version":"shield","text":"Being bitten by a Shellder shocked this Pok\u00e9mon into standing on two legs. If the Shellder lets go, it seems Slowbro will turn back into a Slowpoke."}],"evo":{"name":"slowpoke","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"slowbro","level":1,"min_level":37,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"slowking","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"trade","item":null,"held_item":"kings-rock","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/80.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/80.png","capture":75,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"defense":2},"forms":[{"id":10071,"name":"slowbro-mega","sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10071.png"},{"id":10165,"name":"slowbro-galar","sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10165.png"}]}